  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301472</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>これであの弱虫も、
勝手に外へ出るなどの
わがままはしなくなる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That coward is too wrapped up in
his own personal delirium to face
the outside world and help you.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301568</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;は
弱虫なんかじゃない！
きっと……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's not true! &lt;Dio&gt;
isn't a coward! He...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301756</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>知らなくてもいいことを知り、
歪むくらいなら
何も知らない方が幸せだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Know nothing and shut your eyes to
the world. He's happy with staying
ignorant. It's a simple way to live.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301756</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おまえとて、外の世界に
出るのは不安だったのだろう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're trying to embrace this world, but in
the end, all that's inside of you is insecurity.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301880</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……たしかに、すごく不安だけど
それを乗り越えるのが
楽しいっていうか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...It's true I'm very scared, and sometimes
I get lost, but overcoming all of that's
what made this journey worth it...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302008</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……よくわからないけど、
だからこそ、そこに新しいもの
を見つけられる気がして</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...I can't easily put it into words, but there are
many things I want to see. Everything new in
this world teaches us and makes us stronger...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302072</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>違う、かな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's what I...think...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302148</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……うん、そう、だと思う</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes...I'm sure. That's what I belive.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302212</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……ふん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hmph.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302276</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>きゃあっ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Aaaah!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302340</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kururu!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302404</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mel&gt;……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Mel&gt;, are you okay!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302528</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>家でおとなしくしていれば、
こんな恐ろしい目に
遭わなくても済むものを</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You wouldn't have to suffer this much
if you would have obediently stayed
inside your house.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302608</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それ以上、&lt;Mel&gt;に近づくな！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Stay away from &lt;Mel&gt;!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302668</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mel&gt;！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Mel&gt;!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302732</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302824</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mel&gt;を傷つけたりしたら、
ひどいぞ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I won't forgive anyone who hurts her!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302888</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt;! You came...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302952</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>やるか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Fine. Be that way...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
